Last Updated: January 2025
Effective Date: Immediately

1. Introduction

Welcome to PomodoX ("the App").
PomodoX is a productivity tool that uses the Pomodoro Technique to help users manage their time effectively.
Your privacy is important to us, and this Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data.

2. Information We Collect
2.1 Personal Information

We do not collect or store any personal data such as name, email, phone number, or location.

2.2 Usage Data

The App may locally store the following data on your device:

Number of completed Pomodoro sessions

Selected timer settings

Theme preferences

Onboarding completion status

This data is stored locally (on your device only) using storage mechanisms like AsyncStorage.
We do not send or collect this data on any server.

3. Data Storage and Security

All stored data is saved locally on your device.
We do not transfer or process any data on external servers.
You have full control of app data and can delete it anytime by uninstalling the app or clearing its data.

4. Third-Party Services

PomodoX does not integrate any third-party frameworks, analytics tools or advertising SDKs that collect personally identifiable information.

5. Children's Privacy

PomodoX is designed for general use and does not target children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect any personal data from children.

6. Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time.
Changes will be reflected here and updated with a new "Last Updated" date.

7. Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, feel free to contact us at:

Email: [your-email@example.com
